---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="如何去盐湖 - 盐色运城" description="运城七彩盐湖交通导航：自驾、公共交通、骑行路线全攻略。含坐标定位，点击即可调起地图导航。">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <a href="/saltlake" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-stone hover:text-amber-dark transition-colors mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        返回盐湖主页
      </a>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">如何去盐湖</h1>
      <p class="text-stone text-lg">无论从哪个方向来，找到去盐湖的最佳路线</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 坐标卡片 -->
    <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brick/5 to-amber/5 border border-salt-dark/10 mb-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">七彩盐湖景区</h2>
          <p class="text-stone">山西省运城市盐湖区解放南路 · 盐湖大道沿线</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-3">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white rounded-full text-sm font-mono text-stone border border-salt-dark/10">35°01'N, 111°00'E</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-pool/10 text-pool text-sm rounded-full">全年开放</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=111.00,35.01,七彩盐湖景区&mode=car&callnative=1"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-brick text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-brick-dark transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-brick/20 shrink-0"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0121 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 01-.553-.894L15 7m0 13V7"/></svg>
          调起导航
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 交通方式 -->
    <div class="space-y-10">
      <!-- 自驾 -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2 rounded-lg bg-amber/10 text-amber">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7h8M8 11h6M3 17l1-3h16l1 3M5 17h14v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H6a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink">自驾前往</h2>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-pool/10 text-pool text-xs rounded-full">推荐</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 ml-11">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brick/10 text-brick flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">导航设置</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">在高德/百度地图搜索"七彩盐湖景区"或"运城盐湖"，选择"运城盐湖（中国死海）景区"。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brick/10 text-brick flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">市区出发</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">从运城市区出发，沿解放南路向南直行约5公里即到，车程约15分钟。沿途有"盐湖景区"路牌指示。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brick/10 text-brick flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">高速到达</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">G5京昆高速→运城出口→解放南路向南→盐湖景区。G59呼北高速→运城北出口→机场大道→解放南路向南。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brick/10 text-brick flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">停车信息</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">景区入口设有免费停车场，可容纳约200辆车。旺季（五一、十一）建议早到，停车场可能饱和。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 公共交通 -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2 rounded-lg bg-pool/10 text-pool">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 14v3m4-3v3m4-3v3M3 21h18M3 10h18M3 7l9-4 9 4M4 10h16v11H4V10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink">公共交通</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 ml-11">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-pool/10 text-pool flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">公</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">市内公交</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">乘坐<strong>21路</strong>公交车，在"盐湖景区"站下车即到。从市中心南风广场出发约30分钟。票价：2元。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-pool/10 text-pool flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">铁</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">火车/高铁到达</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1"><strong>运城北站</strong>（高铁）：出站后打车约20分钟到景区，费用约25元。或乘7路公交到市区换乘21路。<br/><strong>运城站</strong>（普速）：出站后打车约15分钟，费用约15元。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-pool/10 text-pool flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">✈</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-ink">飞机到达</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1"><strong>运城张孝机场</strong>：距景区约12公里，打车约25分钟，费用约30-40元。无直达公交，建议打车或租车。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 骑行 -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="inline-flex p-2 rounded-lg bg-salt-pink/10 text-salt-pink">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink">骑行路线</h2>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-salt-pink/10 text-salt-pink text-xs rounded-full">本地推荐</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 ml-11">
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <p class="font-medium text-ink mb-2">盐湖绿道（全程约20公里）</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone leading-relaxed">从七彩盐湖景区出发，沿盐湖绿道向东骑行，途经观景台、盐池神庙、骑行驿站。全程约20公里，平坦路面适合休闲骑行。</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-3 text-sm">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-stone"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>约1.5小时</span>
              <span class="text-stone">自行车租赁：约20-40元/小时</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-salt border border-salt-dark/5">
            <p class="font-medium text-ink mb-2">市区骑行路线（约8公里）</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-stone leading-relaxed">从南风广场出发，沿解放南路向南直行，经过运城学院后继续向南，约20分钟可到盐湖景区。沿途有非机动车道，路况良好。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 地图占位 -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">位置示意</h2>
      <div class="aspect-[16/9] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-salt-dark/10 to-amber/10 border border-salt-dark/10 flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-brick/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-brick" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-ink">七彩盐湖景区</p>
          <p class="text-stone/50 text-sm mt-1">运城市盐湖区解放南路南端</p>
          <p class="text-stone/30 text-xs mt-2">地图组件加载中（需接入高德/百度地图API）</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 简易方位标注 -->
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-xs text-stone/30">
          <p>北 ↑</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-xs text-stone/30">
          <p>← 市区方向（5km）</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="/saltlake" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white border border-salt-dark/20 text-ink rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-salt transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        返回盐湖主页
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
